            <li>You can edit or delete your profile anytime.</li>
            <li>You can request the removal of your data from our database.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>6. Changes to This Policy</h3>
        <p>We may update this policy periodically. Significant changes will be communicated to users.</p>
        
        <h3>7. Contact Us</h3>
